...}, returns a list of dressed Majorana fermion operators \\[CapitalSigma]j \
mij cj, where m is a complex matrix. BravyiElements[m, {a1, a2, ...}] for \
Dirac fermion modes {a1, a2, ...}, returns the equivalent Dirac fermion \
representation of the dressed Majorana fermion operators \\[CapitalSigma]j \
mij cj, where ck are Majorana fermion modes corresponding the Dirac fermion \
modes.", "synonyms" -> {}, "tabletags" -> {}, "title" -> "BravyiElements", 
